topic.title: Ham Radio vs World Hacking Radio experiment !
topic.body:
Hello hackers,
French Live-DVD Gnu-Linux HamBrew (Debian 8.1)
http://radiobxi.org/blog/hambrew-un-live-dvd-gnu-linux-debian-pour-radioamateur/
Receiving voice and data HF/VHF/UHF = RTL-SDR TV dongle and more HF receivers SDR !
Encoding/Decoding data = RTTY (marine weather bulletins, etc.), PSK, FAX, Packet, etc.
Satellites Tracking = International space station, cubesats, amsat-oscar, noaa sats, military sats, etc.
And more ..
73's
